name: Threshold | Lighten_Pp
description:
• Profile Picture
• 1537x2048

📢 I've already crossed barriers that seemed insurmountable.  I exceeded my limits.  But there is always a new me to be the next day.  Being who I am every day and yet knowing so little about me.  Every day I'm taking a new step, trying to be better, stumbling, learning to love my best, being generous with my processes, and exercising patience.  I have been allowing myself to know the limits of my mutated body.  This fickle self of mine.

 It sucks to live, but it sucks even more not to feel.  And I feel, because I'd rather feel and make sense of what escapes my senses – my inner madness, my fears and my wounds – than live pretending it doesn't hurt.  Because it hurts.  And everyone knows it.  Despite everything I remain.
